articles.title: Lamine Yamal: Spain beats France to reach Euro 2024 final after historic goal from 16-year-old - CNN
articles.description: Lamine Yamal made history by becoming the youngest goalscorer in European Championship history as Spain edged past France 2-1 to reach Sunday’s Euro 2024 final.
articles.content:
Lamine Yamal made history by becoming the youngest player to score in a mens European Championship as Spain edged past France 2-1 to reach Sundays Euro 2024 final.
